Introduction

Níng Yìzhuō, known under her stage name NingNing is a Chinese singer-songwriter, dancer, and composer under SM Entertainment. She is best known as one of the main vocalists and the maknae of the girl group aespa.

In September 2016, she was part of the "Who's the best?" segment of My SMT along with fellow rookies Koeun, Hina, and Yiyang. Later in 2017-2018, she along with actress Park Jung Yeon, Koeun and Hina sang several OST for the MBC animated series Shining Star.

On November 8, 2020 Ningning was the fourth and last member of aespa to be revealed. She debuted on November 17, 2020 with the group's first single album "Black Mamba".
